{"tid":115052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士未停定　老翁上層滾落樓梯傷","createTime":"2017-02-10T09:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T11:52:42.000Z","uid":122,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57369bd6884dda2771472830e8ec22716df6f2fb","tid":115052,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>巴士未停定　老翁上層滾落樓梯傷</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170210/photo/bkn-20170210132504391-0210_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170210145230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170210%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170210132504391-0210_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170210145230&h=ebce942f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角發生巴士乘客滾落樓梯意外。下午1時許，一輛九巴沿彌敦道往深水埗行駛，至旺角道附近準備埋站，期間一名坐於上層的老翁擬起身下車，惟在梯間失重心跌倒，繼而滾落下層受傷。車長見狀立即停車及報警，並安排所有乘客離開車廂。救護員到場，將老翁送院治理，當時他仍然清醒。<br />\n<br />\n東網讀者李先生剛好經過上址，目擊事件經過稱：「當時砰一聲，望到入面有個人跌左落嚟，司機就停車，開車門已經睇到位老伯瞓左係到。」"},{"pid":"c88e2aa136b28b92a7de1894f1b759238be17253","tid":115052,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:25:12.000Z","msg":"死廢老就好心咪撚上上層啦"},{"pid":"4e95b9617eb1fd7371a8aae404fa22bcfc3ee779","tid":115052,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42db1af2e071e0dbda31862928aaf43df15fd79a","tid":115052,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"上車又爭位坐<br />\n落車又爭位出"},{"pid":"df7172cdccf7c042da9121bef04ba978b72c09e0","tid":115052,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"老廢重要走上樓上, 我地後生已經唔敢坐樓下架啦"},{"pid":"bfef84f526c4a656887e8a1ae672c038b5323257","tid":115052,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:31:56.000Z","msg":"認真 等巴士停定先起身既話 落到去門口就已經開左車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc021948c8dba145860bead9feaa15dfdac7f07","tid":115052,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死廢老就好心咪撚上上層啦</blockquote><br />\n幫手講咗 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36de5fc9ea50c24372a1c31e5a2288209df6b44","tid":115052,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"廢老無力就咪撚學上上層啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb45289af6edd2151f11f7b8c4a1562a24156b7","tid":115052,"uid":27952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯左 老翁滾上上層樓梯傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdac1515b4484ca83a8123e5adab640c0e2da0b","tid":115052,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"廢老爭住去死"},{"pid":"9223443cd73a15806faca54140ac273c72b5d904","tid":115052,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"以前返工坐上層<br />\n<br />\n見到個中學雞上到最尾個級<br />\n<br />\n個司機一開車佢就碌返落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8479a8ec917c6e682fc325a27d9812c48beb5bce","tid":115052,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"jason 張呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊happy下"},{"pid":"a88532ddb446bd0e24de5a6bd4d7c3cc10ac0d05","tid":115052,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"廢老<img